{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A puzzle game\u00a0</strong>about <strong>sliding</strong> <strong>seals</strong>\u00a0- a more <strong>complex</strong> <strong>challenge</strong> than it initially seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>goal</strong> is to get all the <strong>animals</strong> to their <strong>bubbles</strong>\u00a0by<strong> sliding</strong> the<strong> seals.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>challenge</strong> is to keep all the seals <strong>connected</strong> and the small animals <strong>out</strong> of the water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you <strong>slide</strong> a seal the other animals <strong>react</strong> in their own <strong>different</strong> ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore <strong>surprising</strong> ways to <strong>maneuver</strong> the animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each puzzle explores a <strong>different</strong>\u00a0idea in this <strong> puzzle game</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>195 Hand crafted puzzles ranging from easy to hard </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6 Different animals with unique behaviour</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>7 Different environments</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hand drawn artwork</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534620/extras/PiecesShow.png?t=1731336263\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Each Animal Moves Differently</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heart</strong> <strong>Seals </strong>can be dragged length ways and carry animals on top of them. They like to stay connected and help all the other animals get to their <strong>Bubbles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bears</strong> grab onto the head and tail of the <strong>Heart</strong> <strong>Seals</strong> and get dragged around with them. They are also a safe place for the <strong>small animals</strong> to rest on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Jellyfish\u00a0</strong> are also dragged around by the <strong>Heart</strong> <strong>Seals</strong>, however they like to bounce <strong>small animals</strong> that land on top of them one extra square.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Penguins </strong>are happy to relax in one spot unless moved around by another <strong>animal</strong>. However, they are useful when they <strong>bounce</strong> other <strong>small animals</strong>\u00a0one square forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Foxes </strong>run to the other side of the <strong>Heart Seal</strong>. If there is a small animal in its way, the\u00a0<strong>Fox</strong> will bounce that animal one square forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bunnies</strong> jump to a <strong>Heart</strong> <strong>Seal\u00a0</strong>that moves beside it. They like to <strong>bounce </strong>other <strong>small animals</strong> around to new locations. They can also <strong>collide </strong>with other <strong>Bunnies</strong> that are jumping to the same square.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bear Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1534620/093305c6e85635ea4f8d63fd4b58eacbbacb2987.jpg"},{"name":"Penguin Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1534620/fd46b0ac123527092814ac01968538b4a2dc6335.jpg"},{"name":"Jellyfish Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1534620/182ab8e1e8ccb3ec2c21d41fe0e2210b36c42ff2.jpg"},{"name":"Fox Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1534620/597741a7acd41c475640e99c3e99808ec54ec0bd.jpg"},{"name":"Bunny Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1534620/31bb735404cc6b1d679c8e871bc8e75d45003e09.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https: